name: I'm a Celebrity: Get Me Out of Here!
original_name: I'm a Celebrity: Get Me Out of Here!
overview: Australian celebrities are dropped into the African jungle with little more than their wits, strength and willpower to survive the competition. How will they cope with African wildlife, a constant series of challenges and tests, basic rations and their fellow campmates? Who will survive the infamous Bush Tucker Trials? Who will win the hearts of viewers and be crowned King or Queen of the Jungle?

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: It's day two in the jungle and some of the celebrities have had more trouble than others getting use to giving up their five-star lifestyles. Hosted by Dr Chris Brown and Julia Morris.

episodes.name: Episode 5

episodes.name: Episode 6 (Live Eviction)
episodes.overview: The celebrities have survived their first week in the jungle. The camp site isn't quite a holiday oasis with cocktails whipped up at the snap of a finger. Who is thriving and who is barely surviving?

episodes.overview: With the abundance of animals roaming Africa, most species depend on safety in numbers rather than hiding from predators. The animals are smart enough to form alliances but are the celebrities?

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Kruger National Park is most famous for its large carnivores: lions, leopards, cheetahs, hyenas and wild dogs. Here's hoping the celebrities are a bit tougher than their headshots make them out to be.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: The celebrities have almost survived their second week and should start thinking about how to strategise. It may be a good idea to look to their jungle neighbours for advice.

episodes.name: Episode 11 (Live Double Eviction)
episodes.overview: Having been tested both physically and mentally, the celebrities have fought hard to secure fresh food and special privileges, but in this episode, another celebrity will leave the jungle.

episodes.name: Episode 12 (Intruders Special)
episodes.overview: The celebrities have little time to adjust to losing yet another one of their camp mates as they embark on this episode's Tucker Trial and Chest Challenge.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: With their daily rations becoming increasingly bland, the celebrities are desperate to win extra food and treats for the camp. This episode, they are faced with a Twisted Takeaway Tucker Trial.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: This episode's Tucker Trial, Jungle Jive, will give one of the celebrities the opportunity to hit the dance floor. But little do they know, there is a massive twist.

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: It is Triple Threat Thursday and the High Rollers Tucker Trial will see two celebrities pushed to their limit. Later, the celebrities will have to prove themselves in a Chest Challenge.

episodes.name: Episode 16 (Live Eviction)

episodes.name: Episode 17
episodes.overview: The celebrities haven't received any pampering or comforts since entering the jungle but tonight one lucky celebrity will be given the opportunity to experience various treatments in the Safari Spa.

episodes.name: Episode 18

episodes.name: Episode 23

episodes.name: Episode 26 (Live Eviction)
episodes.overview: After six gruelling weeks, the hunger, tears and trials reach an explosive conclusion, with live evictions as we count down to crowning the King or Queen of the Jungle.

episodes.name: Episode 27 (Live Eviction)
episodes.overview: Chained inside a large tank by their feet, hands and waist, one celebrity must escape their watery bounds in the flash flood Tucker Trial.

episodes.name: Episode 28 (Live Eviction)

episodes.name: Finale
episodes.overview: After six weeks in the remote South African jungle, 14 celebrities have been whittled down to three. This climatic finale will see the first King or Queen of the Jungle crowned live!
